  "name": "RPlog_Sweet_Home_Corellia",
  "title": "Reunion on the Coronet Tarmac",
  "summary": "At the bustling Coronet spaceport on an Imperial-occupied Corellia, the gruff smuggler Alac lounges by his ship after a recently completed job, while the flamboyant Starlight Studios actor Wynn Ryder strolls in and immediately begins charming the crimson four-lekku Twi'lek Ka'una. As Wynn lays on his theatrical seductions and secures a date with Ka'una for the next day, the masked antiquities dealer Geophreigh Smitherbodkins approaches Alac, confirming that Alac's 'indiscreet' assassination of his guest the previous night is done and paying him for the work. When a nervous Imperial trooper overhears the incriminating talk and reaches for his blaster, Alac coldly forces him to surrender his weapon and slink away. Alac's twin brother Alban emerges hungover from the ship, and the trio of old childhood friends, Alac, Alban, and Wynn, reunite joyfully under Smitherbodkins's calculating eye. Talk turns from a planned party to a half-serious scheme to fund a rebellion and take Corellia back from the Empire, with Wynn promising to involve his backers before dashing off to set, leaving the brothers to begin gathering an army.",
